The '''''Canadian Mathematical Bulletin''''' ({{lang-fr|Bulletin Canadien de Mathématiques}}; print: {{ISSN|0008-4395}}, online: {{ISSN|1496-4287}}) is a [[mathematics journal]] published by the [[Canadian Mathematical Society]]. It is published four times per year. The current [[Editor-in-chief|editors-in-chief]] of the journal are [[Jie Xiao]] and [[Xiaoqiang Zhao]].<ref>[http://cms.math.ca/Docs/commlist.html#cjmcmb-board], retrieved 2014-10-24.</ref>  The journal publishes short articles in all areas of [[mathematics]] that are of sufficient interest to the general mathematical public.

